{"tid":2017970,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥表明不會成立獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2020-05-15T10:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T11:12:33.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c85e890c9ada55bdf059f8444bbcda7f15bc10ba","tid":2017970,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:54:13.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥表明不會成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n15.05.2020 18:50<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表明，不會成立獨立調查委員會，特區政府不同意另外成立委員會調查，尤其警方在一連串大型示威活動進行執法工作，她不認同亦不會做，又指事件已變質成以暴力威逼政府滿足他們要求，削弱警隊更令暴力份子得逞。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，很想做獨立檢討委員會，原本邀請數位人士擔任主席及委員，但其後這些人士拒絕，因為「見到同政府有關或看似支持工作，都無乜好下場」，包括擔心自己及家人起底、店舖被「裝修」、出街被「私了」。她質疑在這些環境下難以挺身而出，指過去一年來的事件，不但對經濟及鐵路造成傷害，亦是對公民及文明社會的傷害，要一段時間才能癒合。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287742&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1287742%26csid%3D261_341&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=742ea345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287742&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"8f0fba431a6ea42cb390e436047a3a09e0c8cc94","tid":2017970,"uid":23560,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"有心做嘅晨早做撚咗啦<br />\n洗撚等到今時今日至出嚟講經？"},{"pid":"485ce92d0559633d93cc66c8f47ec41a6be3af34","tid":2017970,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:55:37.000Z","msg":"根本係柒婆唔想靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43120f6f7eb82ce45cf514ffa0842835a4e2b71","tid":2017970,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:56:00.000Z","msg":"衰撚過伊拉克，講完"},{"pid":"5588649e363571a63d996ae3ea66bba0aaf7efe5","tid":2017970,"uid":2545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"485ce92d0559633d93cc66c8f47ec41a6be3af34","tid":2017970,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"rep